      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was prescribed some diazepam to help with my sleep issues but lately ive been having a hard time falling asleep even with the pill. would it be okay if i had like a glass of wine with it tonight to help me relax more? i just want to make sure it's safe for light use.",
