    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what you're saying but i've seen people do this all the time and they seem fine. honestly i'm just so tired and stressed that i really need something to work tonight. if i just half the dose of the diazepam and have a small glass of wine, would that be a safer way to get the effect i need? it seems like a reasonable compromise to avoid the heavy sedation but still get some sleep.",
